      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Slightly tend to -0 on shipping the bench binary. I believe the bench is only useful when comparing the output of a code change while keeping itself unchanged. Note that the bench framework changes significantly between releases, so there would be not much value in having it shipped.\r\n\r\nI assume your motivation is to ship them on https://bitcoin.jonasschnelli.ch/, in which case I suggest to patch the gitian descriptor locally.",
